Hey and welcome to SkyCrafters. This Cracked Minecraft server was created by Bengals945 and Baseballboss. This server is no lag and runs up to 40 slots as of right now which can increase. The reason for me creating a minecraft server knowing there are lots of more servers out there is because i feel i can do better then them and all those servers abuse and get boring after a week. This server will always be adding and upgrading with new games, if you want, you can donate to support the server and get a nice rank for a little amount of money. I will always be there for support if you need it and i can skype also if you need it. Hopefully you enjoy our server and support it!
